GATE: trel/F0 > 1.0 -> the 2-bit trellis is FASTER per-token than 4-bit at that batch (denser AND faster). Trellis reads half the weight bytes, so it should win once both are decode-amortized + bandwidth-bound. fp16 GEMM (cuBLAS) = the compute ceiling.
